(34102,100,0,'Thank you all for attending this sermon. It\'s wonderful to see so many familiar faces!',12,0,100,1,0,0,0,0,'Argent Confessor Paletress'),
(34102,101,0,'Today I would like to touch on the three virtues of the Light.',12,0,100,1,0,0,0,0,'Argent Confessor Paletress'),
(34102,102,0,'These are dark and difficult times for us all. The armies of the Scourge amass to the south. Companions fall on the battlefield and rise to serve our enemy moments later.',12,0,100,1,0,0,0,0,'Argent Confessor Paletress'),
