(34102,104,0,'Yet you persevere, as we all must. In these times, no one is a stranger to the virtue of tenacity. In the face of despair and hatred, we continue to stand true to our beliefs and fight on.',12,0,100,1,0,0,0,0,'Argent Confessor Paletress'),
